Package hu.bme.mit.theta.core.type.anytype

package hu.bme.mit.theta.core.type.anytype
Expressions that work with any type. Use Exprs to create them.

- IteExpr: conditional expression, e.g., if x > 0 then x else -x - PrimeExpr: primed expression, e.g., x' - RefExpr: reference to a declaration, e.g., x

  • Related Packages
    Package
    Description
    hu.bme.mit.theta.core.type
    This package contains types (e.g., Boolean, integer) and expressions operating over them (e.g., Boolean connectives, arithmetic operations), grouped into subpackages.
